Subject: [PATCH 04/40] firmware: arm_ffa: Add ffa_dev_get_drvdata

Signed-off-by: Arunachalam Ganapathy <arunachalam.ganapathy@arm.com>
Change-Id: Icd09d686cab9922563b1deda5276307ea5d94923
